#<AdxTL>@(#)0.0.0.0 $Revision$
# Superviseur
# Gestion du masque CTR8 

$_AFF
If GIMPORT
 Gosub AFF From GSAISIE
Else
 If GMESSAGE <>""
  Gosub ERR From GSAISIE
 Else
  Raz GERR , GZNUM
 Endif
Endif
Return

$HORODAT
Local Date    A_DATE
Local Char    A_HEURE(10) , A_USER(10)
Local Char    A_STAMP(15)
A_DATE  = [09/11/2018]
A_HEURE = "23:03:48"
A_USER  = "DOC"
A_STAMP = "20181109230348"
Return

$TITRES
Return

$VISU
Local Integer A_REPONSE
Global Integer GPRE_VIEW
If dim(A_WINDPREV)<=0 : Local Char A_WINDPREV(30) : Endif
Local Mask CTR8 [CTR8]
Gosub HORODAT
Local Inpbox "CTR8" From GFONCTION At A_STAMP With A_WINDPREV Mask [CTR8] As [SIM_]
Grizo [CTR8]10
Grizo [CTR8]5
Grizo [CTR8]15
Grizo [CTR8]20
Boxact [SIM_]
Gosub TITRES
Boxinp [SIM_] Using A_REPONSE
Close Local Inpbox [SIM_]
Close Local Mask [CTR8]
Kill GPRE_VIEW
Return

$HARDCOP
Local Integer X1(0..14),X2(0..14),Y1(0..14),Y2(0..14)
X1(0)=59 : X2(0)=94 : Y1(0)=1 : Y2(0)=11
X1(1)=1 : X2(1)=58 : Y1(1)=1 : Y2(1)=5
X1(2)=1 : X2(2)=58 : Y1(2)=6 : Y2(2)=11
X1(3)=1 : X2(3)=58 : Y1(3)=12 : Y2(3)=22
Return

$ON_NTFDAT
Onevent BEFORE_AREA Gosub AV_NTFDAT From W1CTR8
Return

$AV_NTFDAT
Chgfmt [M]NTFDAT(indice) With "DZ:"+GFMDAT
Gosub _AFF
Return

$ON_DATLIC
Onevent BEFORE_INPUT Call AS_DATLIC(zc) From W1CTR8
Onevent BEFORE_AREA Gosub AV_DATLIC From W1CTR8
